articles.title: Antim Panghal overcomes heartbreak to win Wrestling Worlds bronze, seal Paris Olympics quota - The Indian Express
articles.description: A day after losing semifinal, Indian teenager beats double European champ Jonna Malmgren of Sweden.
articles.content: When Antim Panghal walked out for her bronze medal match at the World Championships on Thursday, she still wore the look that she had on at the end of her semifinal defeat against Vanesa Kaladzinskay… [+4317 chars]
